        {
            "title": "衛蘭世巡廣州站尾場側田任嘉賓 與過萬歌迷慶祝43歲生日及出道20周年",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"衛蘭世巡廣州站尾場側田任嘉賓 與過萬歌迷慶祝43歲生日及出道20周年\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/43d43c29a270578887cc38fd081f6ed8/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250415/_2025041516104939103.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\">衛蘭世巡廣州站尾場側田任嘉賓 與過萬歌迷慶祝43歲生日及出道20周年</figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>衛蘭《OUT OF FRAME世界巡迴演唱會》首站一連三場於廣州體育館展開並於前日（13日）結束，她與過萬觀眾慶祝43歲生日及出道20周年。演唱會首場邀請到古巨基做嘉賓，第二場則邀請到多年好友側田做嘉賓。兩位人合唱了同曲不同詞的《命硬》及《她整晚在寫信》。側田甫登場，十分興奮，多謝Janice邀請，亦替她感到開心：「終於等到今日，好耐冇見呀，其實我和Janice是青梅竹馬，一同出道，今年是我們共同的20周年！」笑言能夠捱到20年很難得，Janice亦指側田是他第一個想到的嘉賓。\n\n</p><h2>鄧紫棋拍片祝福衛蘭</h2>\n<p>適逢尾場是衛蘭的正日生日，同時是她出道20周年的日子，主辦單位特意送上驚喜，在encore時推出了生日蛋糕，全場近萬位歌迷獻唱生日歌與衛蘭慶生。現場亦播放了一眾藝人的生日祝福，包括G.E.M.（鄧紫棋）、楊千嬅、陳小春、古巨基、側田、回春丹以及一眾聲生不息的女隊，容祖兒、薛凱琪、周筆暢及李宇春。衛蘭表示驚喜萬分，十分感動 。而台下有多位朋友現身支持，包括鍾舒漫、王君馨、泳兒、關心妍、Winka＠Collar、應昌佑、朱芸編及林芊瑩（Irene），場面溫馨。衛蘭非常感謝朋友的祝福：「我一見到他們便哭了，非常幸運20年前有他們的幫助，直到今天仍然陪伴我，十分感恩。」其後，Janice為答謝歌迷們的支持，更再次encore，讓大家即慶點歌，唱出多首經典金典，最後以《大哥》為演唱會劃上完美句號。\n\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4196500/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"Janice 43歲生日，於4月11-13日在廣州開演唱會。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/1b0793634ca79a1d033820f5a33f2a09/2025-04/WhatsApp_Image_2025-04-15_at_15_22_39.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        Janice 43歲生日，於4月11-13日在廣州開演唱會。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4196502/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"尾場，Janice表現得輕鬆而又感動。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/037fdd1b36c86831b19322d0b4dd08f8/2025-04/WhatsApp_Image_2025-04-15_at_15_22_37.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        尾場，Janice表現得輕鬆而又感動。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4196619/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"鄧紫棋拍片祝福衛蘭。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/0e58bd1a7a32e9925d6e73c5e12ebedf/2025-04/WhatsApp_Image_2025-04-15_at_16_02_07_1_.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        鄧紫棋拍片祝福衛蘭。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4196503/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"鍾舒漫、王君馨、泳兒、關心妍、Winka＠COLLAR齊來撐衛蘭！\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/08508709e1dff3ae177ecb86517fd030/2025-04/WhatsApp_Image_2025-04-15_at_15_22_38_1_.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        鍾舒漫、王君馨、泳兒、關心妍、Winka＠COLLAR齊來撐衛蘭！\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4196504/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"關心妍一家前來支持衛蘭，令她十分感動。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/9adf83b4a1d7b05fc88b2fd1de08d01b/2025-04/WhatsApp_Image_2025-04-15_at_15_22_38_2_.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        關心妍一家前來支持衛蘭，令她十分感動。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4196505/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"Janice出道20周年，廣州尾場亦是她43歲的生日正日，與現場過萬位歌迷一同慶祝。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/095f6e0d60a81eefa82e2a0ef32601f2/2025-04/WhatsApp_Image_2025-04-15_at_15_22_38.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        Janice出道20周年，廣州尾場亦是她43歲的生日正日，與現場過萬位歌迷一同慶祝。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4196506/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"衛蘭的歌曲陪著不少人成長。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/09acfddb13ef2379396478cf709cf842/2025-04/WhatsApp_Image_2025-04-15_at_15_22_39_1_.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        衛蘭的歌曲陪著不少人成長。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4196507/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"演唱會首場邀請到古巨基做嘉賓，第二場則邀請到多年好友側田做嘉賓\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/4361435db9b01dd3f34cfd1ad574d0b6/2025-04/WhatsApp_Image_2025-04-15_at_15_22_39_2_.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        演唱會首場邀請到古巨基做嘉賓，第二場則邀請到多年好友側田做嘉賓\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4196508/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"Janice出道20周年，43歲生日，她感激歌迷不離不棄。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/92376c0cc1b8f53848d18350668de9e9/2025-04/WhatsApp_Image_2025-04-15_at_15_22_39_3_.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        Janice出道20周年，43歲生日，她感激歌迷不離不棄。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4196510/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"Janice見到萬人空巷，感動流淚。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/447d0218aff3986727d0e2f2fa71b6fe/2025-04/WhatsApp_Image_2025-04-15_at_15_22_40.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        Janice見到萬人空巷，感動流淚。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
