            "title": "銅鑼灣法拉利行駛中自焚 涉機件故障",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"fb車cam L（香港群組）圖片\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/ecb9c69a1cf3523093ad8384d71c093e/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250415/_2025041515483836349.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\">fb車cam L（香港群組）圖片</figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>今日（15日）早上10時17分，一輛法拉利跑車駛至銅鑼灣高士威道及興發街交界時，車頭突然起火自焚。救援人員接報到場，消防員將火救熄，經初步調查相信法拉利因機件故障引致火警，起火原因沒可疑。事件中無人受傷。\n\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4196532/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"fb車cam L（香港群組）圖片\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/8af9f752f594ae88c68c28442cc48ce6/2025-04/1_0_21.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        fb車cam L（香港群組）圖片\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
